law.history: Repealed 1958 Ky. Acts ch. 121, sec. 46, effective June 19, 1958. -- Amended 1950 Ky. Acts ch. 21, sec. 20, effective Sepember 1, 1950. -- Recodified 1942 Ky. Acts ch. 208, sec. 1, effective October 1, 1942, from Ky. Stat. sec. 681c-16.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Admission of a foreign society to this state; requirements; court review of commissioner's refusal to admit.
